snippet.title: Secret of Qwerty Gameplay
snippet.description:
Secret of Qwerty is available now for Windows here: http://cannibalcat.itch.io/secret-of-qwerty

Survival mode gameplay from our first title, Secret of Qwerty, a typing game inspired by The Typing of the Dead and Dragon Warrior.
